---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Jan Ivkovic";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Jan Ivkovic</h1>
    <small>Full-Stack Engineer</small>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        I am a Full-Stack Engineer interested in various aspects of development and have experience in building servers, web apps, 
        mobile apps, games...
    </p>
    <p>
        The most current projects I have worked on were building a 2D online mobile game with Cloud Base Games Ltd., and in my 
        spare time I am currently building my own chat application using Swift for iOS devices, as I thing the existing solutions
        do not provide enough security and privacy so I decided to build my own simple to use end-to-end encrypted chatting 
        solution.
    </p>
    <p>
        Aside from projects, I am also conducting research at Sophia University (上智大学) in Tokyo, utilizing WebRTC to create 
        a more cost efficient live video streaming solution that could reduce the load on servers and create more efficient 
        live streaming platforms.
    </p>
    <div class="button">
        <a href="/works/">
            <button class="portfolio-button">My portfolio</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Golang" alt="Go" src="https://go.dev/blog/go-brand/Go-Logo/SVG/Go-Logo_Blue.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Python" alt="Python" src="https://s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/pythondotorg-assets/media/files/python-logo-only.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Swift" alt="Swift" src="https://developer.apple.com/swift/images/swift-logo.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Godot" alt="Godot" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6a/Godot_icon.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="C" alt="C" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/18/C_Programming_Language.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="C++" alt="C++" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/18/ISO_C%2B%2B_Logo.svg"/>
        <img width="42" height="46" title="Node.js" alt="Node.js" src="https://static-00.iconduck.com/assets.00/node-js-icon-454x512-nztofx17.png"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="TypeScript" alt="TypeScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="JavaScript" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Nginx" alt="Nginx" src="https://www.svgrepo.com/show/373924/nginx.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Docker" alt="Docker" src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/919/919853.png"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="CSS" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/css3/css3-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="HTML" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/html5/html5-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="Postgres" alt="Postgres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" title="MongoDB" alt="MongoDB" src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/mongodb-icon-1.svg"/>
    </div>
    <div class="skills">
        <ul>
            <li>Golang</li>
            <li>Python</li>
            <li>Swift</li>
            <li>Godot</li>
            <li>C</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>C++</li>
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>JavaScript</li>
            <li>Nginx</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Docker</li>
            <li>CSS</li>
            <li>HTML</li>
            <li>PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>MongoDB</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Lately I am most interested in building servers, networking, cybersecurity, encryption, however, I have also 
        dabbled in building robots, using Raspberry Pis, using/building AI, configuring Linux systems and so on. 
        I enjoy solving problems and building applications which are innovative, new and exciting.
    </p>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    .portfolio-button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #78c2ad;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    .portfolio-button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }

    .skills {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }
</style>
